Description:
ROWLING ON A RIVER
Located moments from the picturesque creekbed in the Arcadia Estate this 558m2 (approx.) is this flat block of land is perfectly positioned and ready for you to build your dream home or investment! And best of all, even after you build your dream home you will still have plenty of room for a backyard.
Located within the development and just a few short minutes to:
- The future Officer town centre;
- Officer and Cardinia Rd train stations;
- Bridgewood Primary School, Officer Secondary College and renowned Officer Specialist School;
- An abundance of parks, reserves and open spaces;
- Freeway access.
If you need inspiration on what to build on this enticing block, scroll through the pictures to see for yourself.
Unbeatable value this beautiful community has something for everyone, titled and ready to go, don't delay in enquiring.

YOUR SEARCH IS OVER!
"Four bedrooms; two living areas; Potter's Grove North estate. Can you ask for more?"
The property is located adjacent to Timbertop and within walking distance to St Brigid's Primary School and public transport. Best of all, it's oh so close to Officer's future retail hub that will make Officer such a popular destination.
The near-new 4 bedroom property has a carefully designed floor plan that includes a bunch of extras that you wouldn't expect to find in your standard home.
The property features:
- 4 bedrooms, master with walk-in robe and en-suite;
- Formal living at the front;
- Open plan living/dining room;
- Stunning kitchen with a walk-in pantry;
- Heating and cooling;
- Double car garage with remote access;
- Landscaped yard, both front and back;
- Alfresco overlooking the backyard.
The property also has additional benefits that will leave you in awe:
- Nine-foot ceilings;
- Upgraded led downlights;
- Floor to ceiling tiles in the bathroom;
- Recess' in the showers. There are so many more upgraded features that you'll simply have to see it yourself to appreciate.
